articles.title: Box Office: ‘Longlegs’ Bedevils With Phenomenal $22.6 Million Debut, ‘Fly Me to the Moon’ Struggles to Lift Off With $10 Million - Variety
articles.description: 'Longlegs,' a Nicolas Cage horror-thriller, out-grossed the rom-com 'Fly Me to the Moon' while 'Despicable Me 4' topped the box office
